{"tid":1505284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建議以後文宣類po係主題同回應都加番出左Po既Link","createTime":"2019-08-25T13:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T13:29:13.000Z","uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"31afd289c353c0d3936609d0aaf59f754723647f","tid":1505284,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:29:13.000Z","msg":"例如果D咩影片圖片<br />\n自己先貼上Reddit / Twitter (至少其中一個啦)<br />\nFB IG同其他果D貼唔貼你地自己決定<br />\n貼完要<span style=\"color: gold;\">貼Link</span>，唔係點幫你推/Retweet<br />\n放一張圖/一段片就有一個Post/Twitter既話<br />\n就會好似遊戲咁，有容易行動既目標，同即時睇到效果<br />\n你貼得上連登就做多步等一眾巴絲容易做野啦<br />\n<br />\n例子：今晚個開槍Post，回覆見到幅圖貼上Twitter，引用回應上埋Link，不過放回覆成日都無乜人睇到係煩D，但引用至少多D機會有人睇到<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/PikachuEXE/status/1165613978392776705\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPikachuEXE%2Fstatus%2F1165613978392776705&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp81NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=5417ba11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPikachuEXE%2Fstatus%2F1165613978392776705&h=01b6a146\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/PikachuEXE/status/1165613978392776705</a>"}]}